Subject: [Caml-list] Merlin, preview version for OCaml 4.10.0

Dear OCaml users,

The Merlin team has released a preview version of Merlin, which is 
compatible with OCaml 4.10.0 .

Merlin is an editor service that provides modern IDE features for OCaml.

This is a preview version:

- the support for short-path is disabled
- only OCaml 4.10.0 is supported in this preview

It can be installed via opam with the usual

 Â  opam install merlin

on an OCaml 4.10.0 switch.

Happy hacking,
Florian Angeletti.
